  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to estimate the incidence and severity of peristomal skin
      lesions and evaluate the progression of the peristomal skin condition at 8-15 days following
      application of the barrier.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
